OL,3,CMen who suppled 'wholesale' heroin and
OL,4,Ccocaine to the South West jailed
OL,6,FFour men have been jailed for
OL,7,Fsupplying "a huge amount" of heroin
OL,8,Fand cocaine to the South West.
OL,10,FJames Lea, 34, from Sparton Close in
OL,11,FGloucester, Omar Hassanjee, 46, from
OL,12,FShirley Road in Birmingham, Mohammed
OL,13,FIshmail, 26, of Woodfield Road in
OL,14,FBirmingham, and James Pokora, 45, of
OL,15,Fno fixed address, were sentenced at
OL,16,FBristol Crown Court on 11 October.
OL,18,FThe sentencing comes following an
OL,19,Finvestigation by the South West
OL,20,FRegional Organised Crime Unit (SWROCU).
