OL,4,Ccocaine to the South West jailed
OL,6,FThe court heard how Lea would travel
OL,7,Ffrom Gloucester to meet Hassanjee in
OL,8,FBirmingham to collect drugs to supply
OL,9,Fto his customers in the South West
OL,10,Fnumerous times in April and May 2024.
OL,12,FOfficers arrested Lea at his home on
OL,13,FSpartan Close on 16 May.
OL,15,FCocaine with a street value of #13,000
OL,16,Fwas seized, along with cash, scales,
OL,17,Fcling film, and other paraphernalia.
