OL,6,FTwo days later officers seized a
OL,7,Fcardboard box from a car being driven
OL,8,Ftowards Birmingham by Pakora
OL,9,Fcontaining 17 blocks of heroin with a
OL,10,Fstreet value of #2.5 million.
OL,12,FLater the same day, #15,000 of high
OL,13,Fpurity cocaine was later seized from
OL,14,Fbeneath the floorboards of safe house
OL,15,Fon Stoney Lane, Birmingham, which was
OL,16,Fbeing cared for by Ishmail.
