OL,6,FHassanjee used his own home on Shirley
OL,7,FRoad in Birmingham to store the money
OL,8,Fmade from the dealing. During a
OL,9,Fsearch, officers found several
OL,10,Fenvelopes and packages containing
OL,11,Fcash, which totalled #65k.
OL,13,FEnvelopes and other packaging at his
OL,14,Fhouse matched that found in Lea's
OL,15,Fhouse in Gloucester.
OL,17,FLea pleaded guilty to possession of
OL,18,Fcocaine with intent to supply and was
OL,19,Fjailed for four years.
