OL,6,FInvestigators said #15,000 of high
OL,7,Fpurity cocaine was later seized from
OL,8,Fbeneath the floorboards of safehouse
OL,9,Fon Stoney Lane, Birmingham, which was
OL,10,Fbeing cared for by Ishmail.
OL,12,FIshmail was sentenced to eight years
OL,13,Fand three months for the supply of
OL,14,Fheroin, and five years and three
OL,15,Fmonths for the supply of cocaine, to
OL,16,Frun concurrently. Pokora was sentenced
OL,17,Fto three years and nine months for the
OL,18,Fsupply of heroin.
