OL,6,FHassanjee, who was found to have
OL,7,Forganised the supply of heroin and
OL,8,Fcocaine across the country, will be
OL,9,Fsentenced at a later date.
OL,11,FDet Con Insp Adam Smith, from the
OL,12,FSouth West Regional Organised Crime
OL,13,FUnit, said officers seized "a huge
OL,14,Famount of class A drugs".
OL,16,F"This group was supplying class A
OL,17,Fdrugs at a wholesale scale, but those
OL,18,Fsame drugs would have ended up as
OL,19,Fclingfilm-wrapped street deals to
OL,20,Fvulnerable drug users in our
OL,21,Fcommunities.
